{"tid":1190991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當年今日：89年6月7日碧街事變","createTime":"2019-06-07T16:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T16:37:51.000Z","uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa879576177fa35180b56283a8145f1371ee632","tid":1190991,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:14:39.000Z","msg":"【當年今日：碧街事變（補充影片）】<br />\n<br />\n1989年6月6日晚至7日凌晨，油麻地爆發一次神秘騷亂，坊間有人稱之為「碧街事變」；<span style=\"color: red;\">事件直接導致7日原本預計150萬人參與、很可能創造歷史的悼念六四死者大遊行，突然被叫停。</span><br />\n<br />\n6月7日的《明報》就這樣描述事件經過，「現場消息說，由於北京最近發生軍隊鎮壓學生事件，連日來每晚不斷有人駕車及徒步沿彌敦道叫口號並遊行叫嚷。今晨一時許，一批為數約十名的男子，部分身上有紋身，分駕多輛掛有十七軍及十八軍字樣的黑布在車上，沿彌敦道往尖沙嘴方向行駛。至彌敦道五五○號龍馬大廈附近時，有一批男子突然跳下車，並狂踢該大廈的大門。此時，適有一輛私家車途經該處&hellip;&hellip;有人襲擊該私家車，並將私家車的玻璃窗擊破&hellip;&hellip;當警員欲上前查問時，遭對方包圍，此時，人群聚集者眾，最高達四至五百人。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">多年後，根據司徒華的回憶錄，當日司徒華曾收到港英首席非官守議員鄧蓮如的電話，告知騷亂背後是一群「別有用心」的滋事者刻意搗亂，而且這群人都是由中國內地而來，要破壞集會。鄧表示因這批人仍未全數被捕，建議他取消集會。在鄧的安排下，司徒華當天早上到電台宣布集會取消。</span><br />\n<br />\n事件真相如何、幕後黑手是誰，動機又是什麼，確實至今仍是一個謎；或許要等某年某日，英國或其他機構的檔案解密，才能找到答案。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;《誰是「碧街事變」的幕後黑手？ （文：李俊峰）》<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2R1rN3r\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2R1rN3r&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=5ee8ce72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2R1rN3r</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;【當年今日．1989年6月6至7日碧街事變】 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2I2GujS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2I2GujS&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=7222e226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2I2GujS</a><br />\n<br />\n#三十年<br />\n#不容青史盡成灰<br />\n#舊時香港<br />\n#舊時香港討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/620177918009590/posts/2713263285367699?s=690569038&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F620177918009590%2Fposts%2F2713263285367699%3Fs%3D690569038%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=8badc982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/620177918009590/posts/2713263285367699?s=690569038&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"c69f65b597d2bdc869ba4b3f19fb35f084509c00","tid":1190991,"uid":85659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:22:53.000Z","msg":"司徒華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b9577e4e427ba218699af921ffbc1fabd91511","tid":1190991,"uid":2429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c69f65b597d2bdc869ba4b3f19fb35f084509c00","tid":1190991,"uid":85659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:22:53.000Z","msg":"司徒華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"幫共匪續命。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc655fd8bf9b0287b8cd2cd83a537ef5fafed20","tid":1190991,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:35:27.000Z","msg":"亞視（舊香港人先知道呢間電視台）既《當年今日》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Yij8ggXnKmE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYij8ggXnKmE&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=3aa835d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Yij8ggXnKmE</a>"},{"pid":"5c512de59649300431311112408eca89dd2c226d","tid":1190991,"uid":41327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dc655fd8bf9b0287b8cd2cd83a537ef5fafed20","tid":1190991,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:35:27.000Z","msg":"亞視（舊香港人先知道呢間電視台）既《當年今日》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n